                        class="inline-block dark:hidden"
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        height="24px"
                        fill="#000000"
                        viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
                        width="24px"
                        ><path
                            d="M480-120q-150 0-255-105T120-480q0-150 105-255t255-105q14 0 27.5 1t26.5 3q-41 29-65.5 75.5T444-660q0 90 63 153t153 63q55 0 101-24.5t75-65.5q2 13 3 26.5t1 27.5q0 150-105 255T480-120Zm0-80q88 0 158-48.5T740-375q-20 5-40 8t-40 3q-123 0-209.5-86.5T364-660q0-20 3-40t8-40q-78 32-126.5 102T200-480q0 116 82 198t198 82Zm-10-270Z"
                        ></path></svg
                    >
                </span>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="md:hidden">
        <div
            class="navbar-burger inline-flex cursor-pointer items-center rounded-md p-2 hover:bg-neutral-300 dark:hover:bg-neutral-500"
        >
            <button aria-label="Open menu button"
                ><svg
                    class="fill-black dark:fill-white"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    height="24px"
                    viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
                    width="24px"
                    ><path
                        d="M120-240v-80h720v80H120Zm0-200v-80h720v80H120Zm0-200v-80h720v80H120Z"
                    ></path></svg
                ></button
            >
        </div>
        <div
            class="navbar-close hidden cursor-pointer items-center rounded-md p-2 hover:bg-neutral-300 dark:hover:bg-neutral-500"
        >
            <button aria-label="Close menu button"
                ><svg
                    class="fill-black dark:fill-white"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    height="24px"
                    viewBox="0 -960 960 960"
